Has any one tried this creek for the putin? Google Map: http://tinyurl.com/d5krmd I paddle Cape<br/>
Fear this past Sunday (1/25/09) and noticed there was a good flow (both cfs and speed) underneath<br/>
the Titan Roberts Bridge. The length of this creek to Cape Fear is about 2.5. The confluence of<br/>
this creek with Cape Fear was wide and poured forth water. Using this as a put-in seems to give<br/>
only 1.5mi of Cape Fear rapids. </div>
